{"tid":505937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓商廈大火29死26傷 民眾要跳樓逃生","createTime":"2017-12-21T16:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T16:59:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b895b571e5aea13994fa11f833261728319fc8db","tid":505937,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513852747_6afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513852747_6afc.jpg&h=7274e523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【更新死傷數字】<br />\n<br />\n南韓堤川市（Jecheon）一棟8層高的商業大廈今日下午發生火災，消防表示至少29人死亡、26人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n商廈內開設有健身中心、餐廳及桑拿浴室等，於當地時間下午4時左右起火。當局表示是商廈停車場一輛汽車首先起火，火勢快速蔓延，消防發言人較早前表示大部份遺體是在2樓的桑拿浴室發現，「火勢及濃煙迅速蔓延，很多人來不及逃生。」<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者稱被困民眾在危急關頭，要由高處跳到消防隊在地面鋪設的氣墊逃生，亦有人跑到屋頂避難，險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n當局派出49輛消防車及60名消防員到場灌救，並會搜尋商廈內是否仍有更多死者。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"79b07e59c359a9698bbbd30d1f92d5dabab8b82d","tid":505937,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"嘉利大廈"},{"pid":"343b573fbb90490a04f5bcbdfbe8276974899ce4","tid":505937,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"國土鍊成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2954a18e315345c668abe0fc8bd60420a2f5d4","tid":505937,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國土鍊成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://blog-imgs-32.fc2.com/o/t/a/otakuisme/200907050009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-32.fc2.com%2Fo%2Ft%2Fa%2Fotakuisme%2F200907050009.jpg&h=6268c1cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}